data.name: CreateCsePersonAccount
CreateDisbursementTransaction
ReadCsePerson
data.value: select top(1) NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadCsePersonAccount
data.value: select top(1) CSP_NUMBER, TYPE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TMST from CKT_CSE_PERSON_ACC where (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (TYPE = 'E')

data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistory
data.value: select top(1) CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, DSS_GENERATED_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, TYPE from CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS where (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (TYPE = 'P')
